    <h1>Typography</h1>
    <p class="text-l color-neutral-600">A fluid type scale based on the Minor Third ratio (1.2), generated with Utopia. All sizes interpolate continuously between 320 px and 1240 px viewports using <code>clamp()</code>.</p>
  </header>

  <section>
    <h2 class="heading-l">Type scale</h2>
    <p>Eight steps from <code>--font-size-xxs</code> to <code>--font-size-huge</code>. The base alias <code>--font-size</code> points to <code>--font-size-s</code>. Use the utility classes <code>.text-xxs</code> through <code>.text-huge</code> to apply sizes in markup.</p>

    
