    <p style="line-height: var(--line-height-s); max-width: 32ch; background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-brand, #0057d9) 8%, transparent); padding: 0.5rem; border-radius: 0.25rem;">Quarterly earnings exceed analyst expectations as the company reports record revenue growth driven by international market expansion and new product launches.</p>
